#   You can use comments in any format you like â€” only lines that contain one of the rules will be interpreted.
#
# List of available rules:
#
#   substitute
#       dev_mode_text  prod_mode_text  file
#
#   copy
#       from  to
#
#   uglifyjs
#       from  to  [common_directory]
#
#   webpack
#       from  to  [common_directory]
#
# =====================================
#
#   Webpack
#       JS:  Babel -> UglifyJS
#       CSS: Minified
#
# =====================================
#
# - .dev files are created automatically, with renaming.
# - Rules are updated only on prod (to_prod), so to_dev always works with the old (previous) rules.
#
